Ask HN: How would you approach an Intelligence Agency to join them
text: Suppose you want to join an intelligence agency, either in UK, US, Africa or otherwise. How would one approach this, are there specific events you need to go to, websites you need to apply to, people you might want to speak to. This should be seen as a diplomatic role in aiding two countries(in most cases you have to be a citizen in respective countries). Has anyone ever successfully interviewed or been approached by some intel?
